Urls to map
===========

Add a new person
----------------

* url /person
* method POST
* adds a person
* code person/insert.ecpp
* body:
    {
        firstname: "firstname",
        lastname: "lastname",
        phone: "345566"
    }

* returns the new id

Update a person
---------------

* url /person
* method PUT
* updates a person
* code person/update.ecpp
* body:
    {
        id: 1234,
        firstname: "firstname",
        lastname: "lastname",
        phone: "345566"
    }

* returns 1 if found, 0 otherwise

Get a person by id
------------------

* url /person/<id>
* method GET
* code person/get.ecpp

* returns a person with id

Get a person by name
--------------------

* url /person/<lastname>/<firstname>
* method GET
* code person/getbyname.ecpp

Get a phonebook
---------------

/phonebook/<id>

method GET
returns the phonebook of the person with id _id_
